Sentencas: Sr2CoTaO6-delta (SCT) double perovskite oxide was synthesized as potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: We systematically characterize its phase structure, thermal stability, thermal expansion, electrical conductivity, and electrochemical performance.
Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The SCT exhibits superior phase stability and high CO2-tolerant properties at high temperatures.
Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of SCT is semiconductor-like and achieves its maximum value of 7 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The average thermal expansion coefficient of SCT in air is 15.0 x 10(-6) K-1 in a temperature range of 30-1000 degrees C.
Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Titulo: CO2-tolerant Sr2CoTaO6-δ double perovskite oxide as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell
